prompt.title: Embedding for Promptbook: AI Integration Made Easy
prompt.content: Promptbook is divided into several packages published from a monorepo. Key packages include @promptbook/wizzard for running books in Node, @promptbook/core for main logic, and integrations with various AI APIs like OpenAI, Anthropic Claude, and DeepSeek.
